neoteroi-mkdocs v1.2.0 (css release asset, styles the OAD-rendered API page)
sha256:f243781dc4c7910ba23e61def0a1b32cbabe59cefb8f4f727789b1066849949c
upstream: https://github.com/Neoteroi/mkdocs-plugins/releases/download/v1.2.0/css-v1.2.0.css

Keep in lockstep with the neoteroi-mkdocs version pinned in pyproject.toml's
docs extra. To upgrade:
  curl -sSf -L https://github.com/Neoteroi/mkdocs-plugins/releases/download/v<NEW_VERSION>/css-v<NEW_VERSION>.css \
    -o docs/assets/css/neoteroi-mkdocs.css
  shasum -a 256 docs/assets/css/neoteroi-mkdocs.css  # update this file
